        Description copied from interface: ProtectionGroups
        Pause the specified proteciton group. This action pauses all periodic snapshot operations and deletion of expired snapshots. Any ongoing snapshot creation or deletion operations will not be paused.

        Asynchronous method overload. Result of the invocation which is a task identifier will be reported via the specified asyncCallback.

        Invocation Result:
        identifier for the task created by this API invocation

        Operation Errors:
        Error - If there is unknown internal error.
        AlreadyInDesiredState - If the protection group is already paused.
        NotAllowedInCurrentState - If there is another operation in progress.
        NotFound - If there is no cluster associated with cluster or protection group associated with pg in the system.
        ServiceUnavailable - If the service is not available.
